1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 22=

3
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:02,560
Chairman, you asked to see me?

4
00:01:03,039 --> 00:01:05,879
Song Zhaoli hasn't shown up
at the office these past few days.

5
00:01:06,359 --> 00:01:07,959
Mr. Song went out of town.

6
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:12,079
You think you're clever?

7
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,560
Not at all.

8
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:20,120
Is he with Ji Xuan?

9
00:01:22,799 --> 00:01:24,079
Six years ago,

10
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:25,840
Song Zhaoli

11
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:28,439
suddenly said
he wanted to sponsor Ji Xuan.

12
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,599
Did something happen

13
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,840
between the two of them?

14
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:43,168
Sir.

15
00:01:43,392 --> 00:01:45,680
This is that girl
who owes money, Ji Xuan.

16
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:48,239
After school, she works odd jobs.

17
00:01:57,239 --> 00:01:58,000
What are you doing?

18
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:58,920
What do you think?

19
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:04,760
Stay back.

20
00:02:04,959 --> 00:02:06,519
Come and try me if you dare.

21
00:02:06,519 --> 00:02:07,879
Let's see who can go all out!

22
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:14,120
Do you think I'm stupid?

23
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,479
You brat!

24
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:16,319
How can you pay me?

25
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,240
Xuan.

26
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,120
Either you kill me today,

27
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,840
or we sign a contract.

28
00:02:27,319 --> 00:02:28,680
I will repay every cent

29
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:31,680
of the money my dad owed you.

30
00:02:39,264 --> 00:02:40,235
(IOU)

31
00:02:42,199 --> 00:02:43,400
Xuan!

32
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:44,759
You're tougher than I am.

33
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,159
Let's do it your way.

34
00:02:47,319 --> 00:02:47,879
Qiu Lin.

35
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,080
Here.

36
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:52,680
Do you think I can live
as strongly as she does?

37
00:02:54,759 --> 00:02:55,360
Definitely.

38
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:17,240
Qiu Lin, drive slowly.

39
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,008
Escort her back to school.

40
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,439
Yes, sir.

41
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:36,159
Chairman.

42
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,759
During that time,

43
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,232
his brother had just died,

44
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,719
and he was depressed.

45
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,616
He happened to see Ji Xuan
being pressured for debt.

46
00:03:47,919 --> 00:03:49,080
That's all?

47
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:50,759
That's all.

48
00:04:07,159 --> 00:04:07,960
What's wrong?

49
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:12,639
I lost the keys.

50
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:14,960
Any clue?

51
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:18,680
That guy's office.

52
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:21,120
Why didn't you tell me yesterday?

53
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:24,920
I slept in the hallway
all night yesterday.

54
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,759
What now? Go find him tomorrow.

55
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,959
I'll change the locks tomorrow.

56
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,272
Such a lightweight.

57
00:04:34,816 --> 00:04:36,279
Yet you still try to drink a lot.

58
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,600
Go to my place tonight,
I'll make you sobering soup.

59
00:04:41,279 --> 00:04:43,240
You can make sobering soup?

60
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:43,959
Of course.

61
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:45,560
I can do anything,

62
00:04:45,959 --> 00:04:47,879
way better than that mortician.

63
00:04:51,639 --> 00:04:52,560
I'm sober now.

64
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:54,519
Save that sobering soup.

65
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:58,000
I never cook, yet want
to make you sobering soup.

66
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,800
Don't you know what it means?

67
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,439
Afraid I'll throw up in your house?

68
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,920
Don't you feel a thing?

69
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,360
When you were kidnapped,

70
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,959
I wanted to turn Qingcheng upside down.

71
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:12,079
Don't you think
our relationship should...

72
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,160
I get it.

73
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:22,160
You're so good to me

74
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,800
because...

75
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:27,439
We should become sworn siblings!

76
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,279
Wu Shu!

77
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,240
You're older than me.

78
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,079
If we really become sworn siblings,

79
00:05:34,199 --> 00:05:36,319
then I would have another elder brother.

80
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:38,680
Can't you really tell?

81
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,279
I like you.

82
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:56,540
Come on.

83
00:05:57,279 --> 00:05:57,779
Go home.

84
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,279
I'll make you sobering soup.

85
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:12,360
What happened so early in the morning?

86
00:06:12,519 --> 00:06:14,496
This morning,
a wall collapsed during construction

87
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:15,800
in the nursing home.

88
00:06:16,079 --> 00:06:17,120
Two workers were killed.

89
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:21,000
What's wrong?

90
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:23,519
Something happened,
I need to go handle it.

91
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:25,439
The surgery is all arranged.

92
00:06:25,759 --> 00:06:26,519
You go ahead.

93
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,720
I'll meet you there.

94
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,180
Okay.

95
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,180
Let's go.

96
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,600
Qiu Lin, wait.

97
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,480
He forgot his phone.

98
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,399
Qiu Lin.

99
00:06:57,560 --> 00:07:00,240
(Song Zhaoli has been
using Qiu Lin's account?)

100
00:07:08,199 --> 00:07:09,439
(His birthday?)

101
00:07:10,368 --> 00:07:12,160
(Enter password. Password incorrect)

102
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:17,120
(Could it be)

103
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,199
(my birthday?)

104
00:07:47,904 --> 00:07:51,552
ظآزThe cycle of fingerprints
left on the coffee cupظآز

